<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Personally I&apos;d read it one essay at a time but there is a continuity to the writing so I think if one read another book in between you would lose the <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Personally I'd read it one essay at a time but there is a continuity to the writing so I think if one read another book in between you would lose the thread of this one...<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
