  <span id="freeText191405022941288696" style="display:none">Started rereading the titular (va-voom) essay to cheer myself up in migraine malaise. Dear God it's <i>so fucking funny.</i> Quite possibly the best essay ever. The spousal overunit moved into another room with his laptop to do homework because when I tried to read out sentence-paragraphs in acquiescence to the demand of 'What's so funny' I couldn't finish for giggling. </span>
