<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6916961-although-of-course-you-end-up-becoming-yourself"><img alt="Although of Course You End Up Becoming Yourself: A Road Trip with David Foster Wallace" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1320553939l/6916961._SX98_.jpg" />
